    <title>hexo常用命令</title>
    <link href="/2024/04/22/hexo%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <url>/2024/04/22/hexo%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>hexo常用命令记录</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="写作"><a href="#写作" class="headerlink" title="写作"></a>写作</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;   &#x2F;&#x2F;layout是scaffolds下的布局-p, –path自定义新文章的路径hexo new draft &quot;xxx title&quot; &#x2F;&#x2F;新建草稿hexo publish [layout] &lt;filename&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;发布草稿<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo clean  &#x2F;&#x2F; 清理缓存hexo g  &#x2F;&#x2F;生成hexo d &#x2F;&#x2F; 构建hexo g -d &#x2F;&#x2F;组合操作hexo s  &#x2F;&#x2F; 启动本地服务<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="调试"><a href="#调试" class="headerlink" title="调试"></a>调试</h2><p>安全模式：不载入插件和脚本</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo --safe<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>简洁模式：隐藏终端信息</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo --silent<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>调试模式：在终端中显示调试信息并记录到 debug.log</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo --debug<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
